race.comment: PAW KRAMER (2) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Hit the frame latest (23.78) when second at Horsham in a Mix 3/4. Has the ability and should feature. TANNER BALE (5) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 0.7 lengths at this track in a handy 22.60 beating Doongalla Nomes. Should feature again. ANCHOR CRANKER (7) was an exceptional 22.53 winner at this track last start. Top win latest and can measure up again. GUNAI WIZARD (1) comes into calculations after placing at this track and distance most recently.
